  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To assess the efficacy, predictability, stability and safety of corneal wavefront-guided
      photorefractive keratectomy (PRK) for correcting hyperopia and astigmatism after radial
      keratotomy (RK).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
